<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Himak nitak fehna hoka ƲIT71</title>
<time_sig>C.M. (8.6.8.6.)</time_sig>
<aka>Il itʋnaha kʋt</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Himak nitak fehna hoka
.    
     Il itʋnaha kʋt,
 Chisʋs chim anumpa hona
.    
     E chim aiahnishke.

[V2]
 Pi Okchalinchi chia ma!
.    
     Pim anukfila ha̱
 Ish pi̱ yohbiehi pulla na,
.    
     Pi nuktaiyalashke.

[V3]
 Chi Shilombish achukma yʋt
.    
     Himak nitak oka,
 Pim a̱ya chi̱ pulla kak o̱
.    
     Ish pim aiahnashke.

[V4]
 Chim anumpa ʋba yokʋt
.    
     Pi chu̱kʋsh pulla ka
 Yohbiecha he mak ona,
.    
     Ish pim aiahnashke.

[V5]
 Yohmi pulla hatukmʋno
.    
     Okla pillikmʋto,
 Ʋba aiachukmaka ya̱
.    
     Il ia hi oke.

[V6]
 Chisʋs ik i̱ yimmo yuk ʋt
.    
     Haknip ʋt illikma,
 Imi shilombish okʋto
.    
     Luʋt ilbʋsha he.

[V7]
 Chisʋs Chitokaka yoka
.    
     I̱ yimmi tok ʋto,
 Aholitopa ʋba ya̱
.    
     Chukowa hi oke.</lyrics>
<author>Israel Folsom</author>
<hymn_number>71</hymn_number>
</song>